original_title: Barney: The Land of Make Believe
overview: Take a trip with Barney™, BJ™, Baby Bop™ and their new friends as they discover anything can happen in The Land of Make Believe! When a puzzled young princess from a storybook magically appears, the group begins a quest to help her find her way home. On the journey, they swim with dolphins, see a beautiful mermaid and even meet a magician! But will the princess ever find her kingdom?
title: Barney: The Land of Make Believe
